{"tid":1978562,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"手足其實只係想贏。。。","createTime":"2020-04-18T19:49:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T19:54:43.000Z","uid":156253,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c1277f6fee7e6421c6a40200f98c7df593394cd8","tid":1978562,"uid":156253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T19:49:57.000Z","msg":"一直都覺得呢個Anita講嘢有盲眼位<br />\n自稱黃絲 但成日喺度批鬥黃圈內嘅人<br />\n佢哋一直掛喺口中就係不斷講人哋如何食人血饅頭<br />\n但手足們其實無在意過比人食饅頭<br />\n手足目的係點樣推倒呢個極權政府 打倒呢10個月以來大家見到嘅不公義<br />\n睇佢嘅留言除咗批鬥 根本就無路線可言<br />\n仲要講話包容藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係以為用左膠方法可以打倒呢個極權政府?<br />\n天琦都有講過條條大路通羅馬 身上背住咁多教條嘅人根本無可能鬥得贏對家 <br />\n如果作為黃絲仍然信Anita嗰套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我認為你哋先係對呢十個月以嚟犧牲嘅手足唔住嘅人<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ARxzhju.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FARxzhju.png&h=4c45054c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"249c5c4a2df368691621536930bc493bb45eeb37","tid":1978562,"uid":156253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T19:52:24.000Z","msg":"自己推"},{"pid":"6dc8e5b880170f658e0fb9f05402aa41485b54bd","tid":1978562,"uid":156253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T19:54:43.000Z","msg":"自己推"}]}